I hope you’re doing well! I wanted to touch base about our hiking trip this coming Saturday. The weather forecast looks promising—sunny with highs around 75°F (24°C). I’ve mapped out a 7-mile loop through Pine Ridge Trail that starts at the Willow Creek parking area. It features a scenic overlook around the halfway mark where we can stop for lunch.

